# Unit Testing

Run unit tests via the Makefile from the repo root:

```bash
# All unit tests
make test

# Focused packages
make test TEST_PKGS="./pkg/controller/v1beta1/inferenceservice/..."

# Single test by name (Ginkgo or standard)
KUBEBUILDER_ASSETS="$(make setup-envtest 2>&1 | tail -1)" \
  go test -v -run "TestReconcile" ./pkg/controller/v1beta1/inferenceservice/...
```

# E2E Testing

Run E2E tests using the scripts under `test/scripts/`:

```bash
# Kind (upstream)
test/scripts/gh-actions/run-e2e-tests.sh

# ODH / RHOAI (OpenShift CI)
test/scripts/openshift-ci/run-e2e-tests.sh
```

## kserve

### Upstream
Utilizes Github Actions from `kserve/.github/workflows/e2e-test.yml`

### Downstream (odh-rhoai)
Utilizes Openshift CI operator from
https://github.com/openshift/release/tree/master/ci-operator/config/opendatahub-io/kserve
Specific configuration (master): https://github.com/openshift/release/blob/master/ci-operator/config/opendatahub-io/kserve/opendatahub-io-kserve-master.yaml

